			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "1) Start new game with Dark Urge\r\n2) Go to Act 3 -> Bhaal Temple\r\n3) Talk to door or oe BTForceOpenDoor\r\n4) Defeat Orin\r\n5) Go through all the post battle dialogs.\r\n6) Depending on choice, will automatically get the netherstone or have to loot Orin's body for the Netherstone Dagger to get the Netherstone.\r\n7) If her stone is the first one before Gortash, dialog will trigger."
				},
